```

---

### 6. File Creation Order and Gotchas

**Creation order matters because of import dependencies:**

1. `src/errors.ts` — no local imports, must exist first
2. Add new interfaces to `src/types.ts` — no local imports beyond existing ones
3. `src/services/product-service.ts` — imports from `../errors.js`, `../types.js`, `../data.js`
4. `src/services/order-service.ts` — imports from `../errors.js`, `../types.js`, `../data.js`
5. `src/routes/products.ts` — replace existing content, now imports from `../services/product-service.js` and `../errors.js`
